  "provenance": {
    "vocalSet": "zh-vocal",
    "correction": "ACE original-poem hook render selected from XL SFT, XL Turbo single-pass, sectioned, repeated, and hook candidates. Active Mandarin timing is based on large-v3 ASR from the selected full mix. This revision uses a sound-close, context-smooth lyric where the render diverges from strict source text: 心爱君兮 is kept because it is consistently audible and beautiful, 君不知 is displayed as 追不着 where ASR/listening indicate that phrase, and 搴舟中流 is softened to 牵愁中流 because the sung line is closer to 前愁/牵愁 than to the rare source character. The original 越人歌 remains the source and emotional frame, but the active website lyric follows the selected performance."
  }
